Sentencas: This paper details the oxidation behavior of coupons from three different Crofer 22 APU sheets.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: Oxidation tests were conducted at 800 degrees C in moist air for 2300h.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: The major features of the scales were similar in all three coupons, with a continuous Cr-Mn spinel layer forming at the gas-oxide interface and a Cr2O3 layer forming at the oxide-metal interface.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: Also, at the Cr2O3-metal interface, large Cr-Mn oxide particles formed in the base metal.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: Metal extrusions in the oxide scale were observed in the vicinity of these Cr-Mn oxide particles.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: All three alloys had internal oxide particles forming in the base metal beneath the oxide scale, and the extent of this internal oxidation was related to the Al and Si-content in the coupons (as also reported by Piron-Abellan J, Huczkowski P, Ertl S, Shemet V, Singheiser L, Quadakkers W.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: Of note, discontinuous Ti-oxide and Mn-oxide particles formed above the outer spine] layer on the coupons with relatively high Al and Si contents.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: The effectiveness of rare-earth surface modification on improving oxidation resistance of this alloy was demonstrated.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: Pack cementation-like processes were used to treat the surface of the coupons with Ce.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: A continuous Cr-Mn outer oxide layer and a continuous inner Cr2O3 layer formed on the surface of the treated coupons during oxidation.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: However, the thickness of the scales and amount of internal oxidation were significantly reduced with the treatment, leading to the decrease in oxidation rate.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: The amount of internal oxidation was also reduced with the treatment.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: The treatment appeared to suppress the formation Of SiO2 at the scale-metal interface in high Si containing alloys.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel

Sentencas: ASR measurements indicate that the treatment decreases the electrical resistance, which is a benefit for SOFC interconnect application.
Titulo: Effect of minor elements and a Ce surface treatment on the oxidation behavior of an Fe-22Cr-0.5Mn (Crofer 22 APU) ferritic stainless steel
